show.description: Psychiatrist Iris Miller’s life unravels when she learns her charming fiancé, Rick Bass, heir to the Bass Group, suffers from dissociative identity disorder torn between Rick the gentle lover and Rick the ruthless tycoon. Refusing to accept this truth, Iris suspects an outside conspiracy and sets out to save the man she believes she knows. As she navigates betrayals from Rick’s scheming stepmother and a cunning business rival, Iris, with the help of her friend Daniel, must confront reality. My Two Fiancés is a gripping tale of love, identity, and acceptance in a world ruled by power and illusion.
